                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-08-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 11, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Poche telegraphs six Armenian naturalized citizens of the United States in prison
                    at Aleppo clamor for more food. A demand for their delivery required by modus
                    vivendi not answered. I believe they are revolutionists.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
